org.concordion.cubano.driver.web.provider

Class RemoteBrowserProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.concordion.cubano.driver.web.provider.RemoteBrowserProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BrowserProvider
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BrowserStackBrowserProvider, SauceLabsBrowserProvider

    public abstract class RemoteBrowserProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements BrowserProvider

    Provides everything required to start up a remote browser (desktop or device) - apart from the where to connect.

    Extend this to provide access to your Selenium grid provider, the framework provides implementations for BrowserStack and SauceLabs.
